Name

C_PIB_COMMERCIAL_ORDER_OPTIONS


Description of the table C_PIB_COMMERCIAL_ORDER_OPTIONS

20-Nov-2022

 

Features and options on the Commercial Order for the equipment. The Sales Order can be linked to an Equipment using IBIN_INSTANCE = equipment CONFIGURATION_OBJECT_NUMBER.

 

View PIB_COMMERCIAL_ORDER_OPTIONS_EQUIPMENT links the Equipment to the Order and Options. PIB_COMMERCIAL_ORDER_OPTIONS_IN_PROCESS is all of the Sales Orders where no Equipment has been generated for the IBIN_INSTANCE.

 

Source: IBINVAL_SEL_F

 

Filter: for type 0002

 

Update Frequency: daily creation or changes
